name: Frame of Hope
description:
My camera and I were exploring an abandoned building looking for something to photograph, but there was no light to be seen.
My hope started to fade until I entered a room where I saw this window as a Frame of Hope.

Black and White Film Photography 

Gear i used 
Camera: Nikon FM10 
Lens: 35-70mm f3.5-4.8
Film: Ilford HP5+
